# Ayron Design System

Ayron is an AI agent for data analytics (connect data sources, chat with an
analytics agent, build dashboards, create automations). Aesthetic: **clean,
technical, dev-tool** — light mode, near-monochrome ink palette, geometric
grotesque type (Geist), generous whitespace, hairline borders, very soft shadows.

Design system root: `design_system/Ayron/`. Project skill: `.cursor/skills/ayron-design/SKILL.md`.

## How to use this system
- **Link the tokens once:** import or `<link>` `design_system/Ayron/styles.css`
  (it `@import`s every token + the Geist / Geist Mono webfonts). Reference
  everything through the `--ay-*` CSS custom properties — never hard-code hexes.
- **Read first:** `design_system/Ayron/readme.md` (full guide), `tokens/*.css` (exact token names),
  `components/core/*` (Button, Input, Badge, Card, Tabs, Switch, Avatar — each has
  `.jsx` + `.d.ts` + `.prompt.md`), `components/icons/Icon.jsx` (Lucide-based set),
  and `ui_kits/ayron-app/` (interactive product kit: chat with artifact panel,
  dashboard, sources, automations).
- Compose the existing components; don't re-implement Button/Card/etc.

## Non-negotiables
- **Light mode only.** Surfaces white / faint gray (`--ay-bg`, `--ay-bg-subtle`).
- **Ink primary:** primary actions are near-black (`--ay-primary`) with white text.
- **One restrained blue** (`--ay-accent`, `#3b6ef6`) only for focus rings,
  selection, links, and the primary chart series — never large fills.
  Semantic colors only in status contexts; charts use `--ay-chart-1..8`.
- **Type:** Geist for UI, Geist Mono for data/metrics/SQL/code. Display & headings
  track tight (-0.02em), weight 600–700. Body 15px / 1.5.
- **Borders do the separation work** (1px `--ay-border`); shadows are soft and only
  for floating/clickable layers. Radii ~8px (`--ay-radius-md`); pills/avatars full.
- **Motion:** quick & restrained (120–180ms, `--ay-ease`). No bounce/spring.
- **Copy:** sentence case everywhere, plain and direct, lead with a verb. Address
  the user as "you". **No emoji** in product UI. Numbers are concrete (metric +
  delta + window), shown in mono.

## States
- Hover: surfaces step one neutral darker; primary buttons → pure black.
- Focus: 3px blue ring (`--ay-shadow-focus`) — always visible.
- Selected: faint blue tint (`--ay-selection-bg`).
- Disabled: `--ay-text-disabled`, no shadow.
